77
78enum form {
79 FORM_SRC = 1, /* Format is mdoc(7) or man(7). */
80 FORM_CAT, /* Manual page is preformatted. */
81 FORM_NONE /* Format is unknown. */
82};
83
84enum argmode {
85 ARG_FILE = 0,
86 ARG_NAME,
87 ARG_WORD,
88 ARG_EXPR
89};
90
91struct manpage {
92 char *file; /* to be prefixed by manpath */
93 char *names; /* a list of names with sections */
94 char *output; /* user-defined additional output */
95 size_t ipath; /* number of the manpath */
96 int sec; /* section number, 10 means invalid */
97 enum form form;
98};
99
100struct mansearch {
101 const char *arch; /* architecture/NULL */
102 const char *sec; /* mansection/NULL */
103 const char *outkey; /* show content of this macro */
104 enum argmode argmode; /* interpretation of arguments */
105 int firstmatch; /* first matching database only */
106};
107
108
109struct manpaths;
110
111int mansearch(const struct mansearch *cfg, /* options */
112 const struct manpaths *paths, /* manpaths */
113 int argc, /* size of argv */
114 char *argv[], /* search terms */
115 struct manpage **res, /* results */
116 size_t *ressz); /* results returned */
117void mansearch_free(struct manpage *, size_t);
